    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite all seven assessed credibility factors achieving levels below required levels and six factors remaining unassessed, the credibility assessment package is accepted as complete for submission purposes. The mesh independence verification activity was declared and documented. Validation results demonstrate model behavior across benchmark operating points. The assessment team acknowledges that the achieved credibility profile does not meet MRL 5 requirements and further evidence generation is required before regulatory submission.",
